1
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,520
[Breaking news.]

2
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:26,240
[Chairman and his wife of Blue Crane Group died in a car accident.]

3
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,880
[Their only heir, Lan Hewei,]

4
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:30,160
[is suspected to have jumped off a building due to shock.]

5
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,680
[She has been taken to the hospital.]

6
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,800
[She is still in critical condition.]

7
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:39,440
[Blue Crane Group, one of the three major groups in the city,]

8
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:42,440
[has halted its key resort development project.]

9
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:44,720
[The board is in turmoil, and the stock price has plummeted.]

10
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:47,720
[Lin Group is acquiring all the floating shares of Blue Crane.]

11
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,680
Where am I?

12
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,000
This is our home.

13
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:05,680
Honey...

14
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,480
Who are you?

15
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,440
I don't know you.

16
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:27,720
This is...

17
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:29,600
even more dangerous.

18
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,440
It seems
that you still don't remember me

19
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,200
after waking up this time.

20
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:37,480
Today

21
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:38,560
is the day we got our marriage certificate.

22
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,480
I've prepared a surprise for you.

23
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,840
Do you remember?

24
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,480
You've been in a coma for over a year.

25
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,160
Now,

26
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:56,080
you just temporarily lost your memory.

27
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,680
Do you remember anything?

28
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:12,320
If you're my husband,

29
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,800
then who am I?

30
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,640
You are my wife,

31
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:32,200
Lan Hewei.

32
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,400
Has the date for Lin Mojiao's marriage

33
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,200
to the Zhu family been set?

34
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:57,680
You good brother

35
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:59,040
set it on the second anniversary

36
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:00,200
when she was killed.

37
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,600
Is he still looking for Lan Hewei?

38
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:04,880
Yes.

39
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,720
We'll let everyone know

40
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:07,840
at the engagement party

41
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,600
that Lin Mojiao and Lan Hewei are married.

42
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,680
Disrupt the marriage between Lin and Zhu.

43
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,360
Start our plan.

44
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,320
She woke up again.

45
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,920
Still doesn't remember.

46
00:04:19,400 --> 00:04:20,160
Her condition is unstable.

47
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,880
You've been pretending to be her husband for so long.

48
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,960
you must be really into her, right?

49
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,840
She's your sister-in-law.

50
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,000
We've had so many chances,

51
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,360
but you keep delaying sending her back.

52
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,640
You must be in love with her.

53
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,480
Don't be soft-hearted this time.

54
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,280
Got it, stop nagging.

55
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:11,320
[The CEO and his wife of Blue Crane Group died in a car accident.]

56
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,760
[The heir Lan Hewei committed suicide.]

57
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,440
[Lin Group took over Blue Crane.]

58
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:18,920
Car accident?

59
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,240
Suicide?

60
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,360
[Lin Group,]

61
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:22,520
[Lanhe,]

62
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,320
[Weiwei.]

63
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,560
Where are you going

64
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,880
in such a hurry?

65
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,680
I don't remember you at all.

66
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,880
Videos and photos can be faked.

67
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,440
They don't prove our relationship.

68
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,480
What do you want?

69
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,120
Since you don't believe me,

70
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:55,000
then I'll

71
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,360
prove it.

72
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:03,360
You're violating my will.

73
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,400
It's against the law.

74
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,880
Your head was badly injured after the fall,

75
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,560
which caused your memory to be messed up.

76
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,000
Am I really a suicide?

77
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,440
Were those fragments just now

78
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,240
all my delusions?

79
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,560
Marriage certificate.

80
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,320
Am I violating

81
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,840
your will now?

82
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,400
I know you're confused right now.

83
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,160
You need your own space to digest it.

84
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,480
Let's take it slow.

85
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,480
I'll always be here for you.

86
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,040
Vivi,

87
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,200
I'll go prepare breakfast for you.

88
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,320
You go back to your room and rest.

89
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,520
What are you doing here?

90
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,840
When did you learn to cook?

91
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,040
Honey,

92
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,360
don't you want to introduce me?

93
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,000
Honey?

94
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,520
How dare you hit me?

95
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,640
Lin Moqing, you bastard!

96
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:02,880
I've done so much for you.

97
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:04,440
I even put the Zhu family on you.

98
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:04,920
But what about you?

99
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,600
When did I say I needed it?

100
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,600
What about the marriage between our two families?

101
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,440
Are you not going to care about it anymore?

102
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,440
If you want to take revenge on Lin Mojiao,

103
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:14,560
marrying me is the best way.

104
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,280
I don't need to use marriage,

105
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:19,200
such a low-level method.

106
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:40,680
Zhu Wenjie is just the daughter of my partner.

107
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,360
No need to explain.

108
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,040
I believe you.

109
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:53,360
You said I lost my memory, right?

110
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:54,680
Today,

111
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:57,280
I want to go for a check-up.

112
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,880
I'll go with you.

113
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,600
I'm not comfortable

114
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,360
letting my beautiful wife go out alone.

115
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,960
If she gets noticed by someone,

116
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:29,320
I'll suffer a big loss.

117
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,320
Okay.

118
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,720
Let's go together.

119
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,440
I'll go prepare clothes for you.

120
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,320
Any news about Lan Hewei recently?

121
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:05,680
Not yet.

122
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:16,440
Look at that.
Does it look familiar?

123
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:20,480
You...

124
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:31,800
I want to go see

125
00:11:31,800 --> 00:11:32,840
the ward I stayed in before.

126
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:37,240
Do you remember anything?

127
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:46,440
Do you remember?

128
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:57,080
Don't touch me.

129
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:06,920
What's wrong with you?

130
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:54,640
I didn't expect you to lose your memory completely.

131
00:14:55,280 --> 00:14:56,600
[You even forgot your own home.]

132
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:11,400
Go home first.

133
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:12,840
I'll pick you up later.

134
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,720
Send someone to Senyuan Hospital

135
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:34,160
to erase Lan Hewei's visit today.

136
00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:12,080
Hello, Mr. Lin.

137
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:39,080
Let's go.

138
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,240
Did you take care of it at the hospital?

139
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:41,960
You can trust me.

140
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:47,360
[Don't let love cloud your judgment.]

141
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:49,280
[This is the critical moment for revenge.]

142
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:54,200
[Don't forget how your parents died.]

143
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:56,520
[To get revenge,]

144
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:59,120
[you've endured so much to get this far.]
